  ::
  ++  ta-know
    :>    story monad
    :>
    :>  produces a gill that takes a gate. if the story
    :>  {nom} exists, calls the gate with a story core.
    :>  if it doesn't, does nothing.
    ::
    |=  nom/name
    |=  fun/$-(_so _ta)
    ^+  +>+>
    =+  pur=(~(get by stories) nom)
    ?~  pur
      %-  ta-evil
      (crip "no story '{(trip nom)}'")
    (fun ~(. so nom ~ u.pur))
  ::
  :>  #
  :>  #  %interaction-events
