  :>    ship+path from wire
  :>
  :>  parses {wir} to obtain the target ship and the
  :>  query path.
  ::
  |=  wir/wire
  ^-  (pair ship path)
  ?+  wir  ~&(wir !!)
      {$circle @ @ *}
    :-  (slav %p i.t.t.wir)
    (welp /circle t.t.t.wir)
