  |=  des/(list delta)
  ^-  (quip move _+>)
  =|  moz/(list move)
  |-  ^-  (quip move _+>.^$)
  ?~  des  [moz +>.^$]
  =^  mos  +>.^$  (bake i.des)
  $(moz :(welp moz mos (affection i.des)), des t.des)
  ::TODO  ideally you'd just do this, but that runtime errors on "bake"...
  ::%+  roll  des
  ::|=  {d/delta m/(list move) _+>.$}
  ::=^  mos  +>.^$  (bake d)
  ::[:(welp m mos (affection d)) +>.^$]
::
++  peek
  |=  pax/path
